title: Acid.Cam.The.Movie.1080p.x264
description:
Acid Cam is a trip through a parallel universe. Where colors morph and thoughts come alive. 

Now you can see Acid Cam the Movie in full bitrate instead of the highly compressed version on YouTube. It also contains a Dolby Digital 2.0 soundtrack. I have been watching this on my 4K HDTV upscaling it to 4K and the quality of the picture is amazing. 

This was created with software and is a software generated animation.
